  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ready to break out?</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bearly Escape is a fast-paced VR action adventure where you play as a brave little bear on the run from a not-so-nice scientist. Use your wits, speed, and special abilities to overcome traps and make your great escape! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3596370/extras/7862263f49408a3e568494a94741b4a2.poster.avif?t=1752725561\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3596370/extras/7862263f49408a3e568494a94741b4a2.webm?t=1752725561\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3596370/extras/7862263f49408a3e568494a94741b4a2.mp4?t=1752725561\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🧪 <strong>Face off against the mad scientist</strong> – Watch chaos unfold as a giant gorilla storms the lab, smashing the villain's machines in an epic showdown. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3596370/extras/ed515327444c13edeb9bf5c968bdcdaf.poster.avif?t=1752725561\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3596370/extras/ed515327444c13edeb9bf5c968bdcdaf.webm?t=1752725561\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3596370/extras/ed515327444c13edeb9bf5c968bdcdaf.mp4?t=1752725561\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 🐾<strong>Stealth and speed matter</strong> – Caught in the wild? Run, duck, and escape before the scientist’s minions grab you! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3596370/extras/8868f0d980ae0fbc424e50ceba33b8c3.poster.avif?t=1752725561\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3596370/extras/8868f0d980ae0fbc424e50ceba33b8c3.webm?t=1752725561\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3596370/extras/8868f0d980ae0fbc424e50ceba33b8c3.mp4?t=1752725561\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎁 <strong>Claw your way to freedom</strong> – Outsmart the twisted claw machine and free your fellow animals from captivity. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3596370/extras/3e449c10ef7351b545fc67d9ae0dce38.poster.avif?t=1752725561\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3596370/extras/3e449c10ef7351b545fc67d9ae0dce38.webm?t=1752725561\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3596370/extras/3e449c10ef7351b545fc67d9ae0dce38.mp4?t=1752725561\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌲 <strong>Dash through the forest</strong> – Leap over obstacles, slide under branches, and survive a series of wild chase sequences in lush environments. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3596370/extras/8277ed52890c0ca9c61602bb2175ea22.poster.avif?t=1752725561\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3596370/extras/8277ed52890c0ca9c61602bb2175ea22.webm?t=1752725561\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3596370/extras/8277ed52890c0ca9c61602bb2175ea22.mp4?t=1752725561\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💥 <strong>Unlock special powers</strong> – Slam, dash, and claw your way through challenges using unique bear abilities. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bearly Escape combines humor, tension, and creativity in a one-of-a-kind VR experience. It’s cute, chaotic, and completely immersive. Are you bear enough to escape?</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ready to break out?</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bearly Escape is a fast-paced VR action adventure where you play as a brave little bear on the run from a not-so-nice scientist. Use your wits, speed, and special abilities to overcome traps and make your great escape! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3596370/extras/7862263f49408a3e568494a94741b4a2.poster.avif?t=1752725561\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3596370/extras/7862263f49408a3e568494a94741b4a2.webm?t=1752725561\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3596370/extras/7862263f49408a3e568494a94741b4a2.mp4?t=1752725561\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🧪 <strong>Face off against the mad scientist</strong> – Watch chaos unfold as a giant gorilla storms the lab, smashing the villain's machines in an epic showdown. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3596370/extras/ed515327444c13edeb9bf5c968bdcdaf.poster.avif?t=1752725561\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3596370/extras/ed515327444c13edeb9bf5c968bdcdaf.webm?t=1752725561\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3596370/extras/ed515327444c13edeb9bf5c968bdcdaf.mp4?t=1752725561\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 🐾<strong>Stealth and speed matter</strong> – Caught in the wild? Run, duck, and escape before the scientist’s minions grab you! </p><p clas