596370/extras/8277ed52890c0ca9c61602bb2175ea22.webm?t=1752725561\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3596370/extras/8277ed52890c0ca9c61602bb2175ea22.mp4?t=1752725561\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💥 <strong>Unlock special powers</strong> – Slam, dash, and claw your way through challenges using unique bear abilities. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bearly Escape combines humor, tension, and creativity in a one-of-a-kind VR experience. It’s cute, chaotic, and completely immersive. Are you bear enough to escape?</p>",
